    <p>All motion respects user preferences for reduced motion.</p>

    <div class="a11y-grid">
      <div class="a11y-card">
        <h4>Reduced Motion</h4>
        <p>For users with vestibular disorders</p>
        <pre><code>@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .spring-animation {
    transition: none;
    animation: none;
  }
}</code></pre>
      </div>

      <div class="a11y-card">
        <h4>Motion Duration Limits</h4>
